---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lang = 'en';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Miguel Padín Domínguez"
  description="Privacy policy for miguelpadin.github.io — how personal data is collected and processed."
  lang={lang}
>
  <div style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 5rem 2rem 7rem;">
    <a
      href={`${base}/`}
      style="
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.4rem;
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: 0.625rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--color-muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      "
      onmouseover="this.style.color='var(--color-accent)'"
      onmouseout="this.style.color='var(--color-muted)'"
    >← Back</a>

    <article>
      <p style="
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: 0.625rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--color-accent);
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
      ">Legal</p>

      <h1 style="
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--color-fg);
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
        line-height: 1.15;
      ">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <p style="
        font-family: var(--font-body);
        font-size: 0.8125rem;
        color: var(--color-muted);
        margin: 0 0 3rem;
      ">Last updated: May 2026</p>

      <div style="
        font-family: var(--font-body);
        font-size: 0.9375rem;
        color: var(--color-muted);
        line-height: 1.75;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
      ">

        <section>
          <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 0.625rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-fg); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">Who we are</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0;">This site is operated by <strong style="color: var(--color-fg);">Miguel Padín Domínguez</strong>, acting as a private individual. For any privacy-related question, contact <a href="mailto:miguel.padin.dominguez@gmail.com" style="color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: none;">miguel.padin.dominguez@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 0.625rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-fg); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">What data we collect</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">This site does not collect any directly identifying personal data such as names, email addresses or forms.</p>
          <p style="margin: 0;">If you consent to analytics cookies, <strong style="color: var(--color-fg);">Google Analytics 4</strong> collects anonymised usage data: pages visited, approximate location (country/city), device type, browser and referral source. IP addresses are anonymised before storage. No data is linked to an identifiable person.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 0.625rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-fg); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">Legal basis</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0;">Analytics data is processed on the basis of your <strong style="color: var(--color-fg);">consent</strong> (Art. 6(1)(a) GDPR), given through the cookie banner when you first visit the site. You can withdraw consent at any time — see the <a href={`${base}/cookies/`} style="color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: none;">Cookie Policy</a> for instructions.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 0.625rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-fg); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">Data retention</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0;">Google Analytics retains aggregated usage data for 14 months by default. No personal data is stored on this site's servers.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 0.625rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-fg); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">Your rights</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0;">Under the GDPR you have the right to access, rectify, erase or object to the processing of your data, and to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority. Since no personally identifiable data is stored on this site, most requests should be directed to Google. To request deletion of analytics data, visit <a href="https://myaccount.google.com/data-and-privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: none;">Google's Privacy Controls</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 0.625rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-fg); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">Third parties</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0;">This site uses <a href="https://analytics.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: none;">Google Analytics 4</a>, operated by Google Ireland Limited (Gordon House, Barrow Street, Dublin 4, Ireland). Google may process data on servers in the United States under the EU–US Data Privacy Framework. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: none;">Google's Privacy Policy</a> for details.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 0.625rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-fg); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">Cookies</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0;">For detailed information about the cookies used on this site, please read the <a href={`${base}/cookies/`} style="color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: none;">Cookie Policy</a>.</p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</Layout>
